{"type": "article", "id": 24671, "title": "线条杂志架", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-30T07:01:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607141018QnIyiXve6S5hPWCY.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款有线条感的杂志架，仅仅用铁棒做成。下面是一个盒子一样的空间放杂物和书籍，然后用一个较大的铁框串起，可以做手提杆或将一本看了一半的杂志扣在上面，很轻盈，也能适应多种环境。有黑白两色，白色的像是隐藏在了白色的墙壁里，也体现出了极简。售价 190 美元，<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/minus-magazine-stand/\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141016LoCxzeYpnHv9ad1Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.41489362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141016w2o0RpzaxMvSEDFY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41489362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141016AhTQ1eNWyoCn26jG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41489362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141017Mgmp6ZKyW2rAPSqt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41489362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141017swmNXcU5BTQDv9gL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41489362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}